title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 9, subtit. J - Division of Human Rights
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 9, subtit. J - Division of Human Rights

State Regulations

Part 465 - Rules Of Practice (§ 465.1 to 465.22)

Part 466 - General Regulations (§ 466.1 to 466.16)

Part 467 - Repealed

Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 9, subtit. J
Pursuant to chapter 958 of the Laws of 1968, the name State

Commission for Human Rights was changed to Division of Human Rights. All
references to the Law Against Discrimination denote article 15 ( §§ 290-301) of
the Executive Law. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
